Tga '''Rracidiya''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵕⵕⴰⵛⵉⴷⵢⴰ''') nɣ s yism nns aqbur '''Qṣar Ssuq''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵇⵚⴰⵕ ⵙⵙⵓⵇ''') nɣ s yism nns amaziɣ '''Imtɣarn''' (s [[tifinaɣ]]: '''ⵉⵎⵜⵖⴰⵔⵏ''') yat tmdint illan ɣ tuẓẓumt-agmuḍan n tgldit n [[Lmɣrib]], twala i tsga n [[Tasga n Dṛɛa-Tafilalt|Dṛɛa-Tafilalt]].

== Imzdaɣ ==
Ar ittini usidn lli ittuyskar ɣ usggwas n 2004 mas tiɣrmt ad zdɣn gis uggar n 41 984 n middn. Akk imzdaɣn n tiɣrmt ad gan [[imaziɣn]], ar sawaln akk gratsn s [[Tamaziɣt n Waṭlas anammas|Tamaziɣt n waṭlas anammas]].

